snippet.title: Sword Art Online: Fatal Bullet | PS4, XB1, PC
snippet.description:
Sword Art Online: Fatal Bullet will test your TPS skills as you traverse the world of Gun Gale Online!  Experience an all new story with original characters Kureha and Zeliska, uncover the mysteries of the ArFA-sys, and become the hero with the all new character customization features!  With multiple skills and appearances at your disposal, you can control your own future.  You are now the hero, and your choice is faster and heavier than a bullet.  

Preorder: http://amzn.to/2w8D8UJ

Follow Bandai Namco Entertainment:
